<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body
    style="
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 0;
      background-color: #f6f7f5;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    "
  >
    <table
      align="center"
      width="600"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      style="
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      "
    >
      <!-- Header -->
      <tr>
        <td
          style="
            background: #005b4c;
            color: #f5e9d6;
            padding: 24px 20px;
            text-align: center;
          "
        >
          <div
            style="
              display: flex;
              justify-content: center;
              align-items: center;
              gap: 6px;
              font-size: 24px;
              font-weight: bold;
            "
          >
            Bottles
            <img
              width="44"
              height="44"
              src="https://bnb-services-7heb.vercel.app/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2FN.df5fd99e.png&w=256&q=75"
              alt="n"
              style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;"
            />
            Boxes
          </div>
          <div
            style="
              margin-top: 6px;
              font-size: 12px;
              font-weight: normal;
              opacity: 0.9;
            "
          >
            Where packaging meets the right partner
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- Body -->
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 28px 30px; color: #333333;">
          <h2 style="color: #005b4c; margin-top: 0;">
            Welcome, <%= name %> 👋
          </h2>

          <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
            We're excited to have you on board as a
            <strong style="color: #005b4c;"><%= role %></strong> on
            <strong>Bottles n Boxes</strong>.
          </p>

          <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-top: 20px;">
            Here's how it works:
          </p>

          <ul
            style="
              padding-left: 18px;
              margin: 10px 0 20px;
              font-size: 14px;
              line-height: 1.6;
            "
          >
            <li>Post your complete packaging requirements.</li>
            <li>Sellers actively browse buyer posts.</li>
            <li>Interested sellers contact you directly.</li>
          </ul>

          <p style="font-size: 15px;">
            And yes — it's all
            <strong style="color: #005b4c;">100% FREE</strong> with no
            hidden charges.
          </p>

          <p style="margin-top: 26px; font-size: 15px;">
            👉 <strong>Your next step</strong>
          </p>

          <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 14px;">
            <a
              href="https://boxesnbottles.com/post"
              style="
                background-color: #005b4c;
                color: #ffffff;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: bold;
                padding: 12px 28px;
                border-radius: 6px;
                display: inline-block;
                font-size: 15px;
              "
            >
              Make a Post
            </a>
          </div>

          <hr
            style="
              margin: 36px 0 20px;
              border: none;
              border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
            "
          />

          <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666; line-height: 1.5;">
            Need help or have questions? Just reply to this email — we're
            happy to help.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <tr>
        <td
          style="
            background: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #888;
          "
        >
          © BNB Services • Bottles n Boxes
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
